snippet: World number one Serena Williams kept her Wimbledon title defense on track on Sunday, downing Germany's Annika Beck 6-3 6-0 with a crushing display of power and booming serves to chalk up her 300th grand slam victory....
lead_paragraph: World number one Serena Williams kept her Wimbledon title defense on track on Sunday, downing Germany's Annika Beck 6-3 6-0 with a crushing display of power and booming serves to chalk up her 300th grand slam victory.

headline.print_headline: Three Hundred Up and Counting as Serena Powers Through
